se-study-eu-industries-china-trade-spat-2024-06-24/</link><description>行业高管表示，受到中国关税的打击，澳大利亚葡萄酒行业尽管忙于开拓新市场、从其他地方采购葡萄并寻求政府帮助，但仍难以抵消出口下降的影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:22:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/australian-wine-sector-worrying-case-study-eu-industries-china-trade-spat-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：随着半年临近，跨大西洋分裂重新开放</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-24/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:17:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>德国安联投资中国大型养老金公司2%股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/german-allianz-invest-chinas-mega-pension-company-with-2-stake-2024-06-24/</link><description>德国保险公司安联旗下的投资部门之一安联全球投资公司（AGI）已成为第一家持有中国养老保险巨头国民养老金股份的外国公司。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 09:35:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/german-allianz-invest-chinas-mega-pension-company-with-2-stake-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫称俄罗斯正在修改其核理论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-is-revising-its-nuclear-doctrine-kremlin-says-2024-06-24/</link><description>克里姆林宫发言人德米特里·佩斯科夫周一援引总统弗拉基米尔·普京早些时候的声明称，世界上最大的核国家俄罗斯已开始更新其核理论。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 09:34:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-is-revising-its-nuclear-doctrine-kremlin-says-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>卢比受到预期资金流入的支撑，但受到亚洲同行疲软的抵消</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-underpinned-by-expected-inflows-countered-by-weak-asian-peers-2024-06-24/</link><description>印度卢比周一基本持平，因人民币和日元疲软抵消了与国内债券相关的美元流入被纳入摩根大通指数的预期。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 07:19:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-underpinned-by-expected-inflows-countered-by-weak-asian-peers-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>韩国电池厂火灾造成22名工人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/about-20-bodies-found-after-fire-south-korea-battery-plant-yonhap-reports-2024-06-24/</link><description>消防官员称，周一，韩国一家锂电池工厂发生多次强烈爆炸，起火失控，造成 22 名工人死亡，其中大多数是中国公民。火灾失控了近 6 个小时。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 07:05:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/about-20-bodies-found-after-fire-south-korea-battery-plant-yonhap-reports-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾指责中国使用“非法武力”故意扰乱补给任务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-continue-south-china-sea-resupply-missions-defense-sec-says-2024-06-24/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长表示，中国使用“侵略性和非法武力”扰乱了在南海的补给任务，并表示上周造成一名水手受伤的海上事件既不是误会，也不是意外。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 06:58:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-continue-south-china-sea-resupply-missions-defense-sec-says-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>英国高级法官在外国法官争吵中审理香港抗议案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/top-british-judge-hears-hong-kong-protest-case-amid-foreign-judges-row-2024-06-24/</link><description>周一，一名英国高级法官在香港审理了一起涉及七名知名民主党人的抗议相关案件，加剧了关于外国法官是否应该在国家安全镇压期间继续担任香港最高法院法官的争论。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 05:44:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/top-british-judge-hears-hong-kong-protest-case-amid-foreign-judges-row-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国字节跳动与博通合作开发先进人工智能芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinas-bytedance-working-with-broadcom-develop-advanced-ai-chip-sources-say-2024-06-24/</link><description>两位知情人士称，中国字节跳动正在与美国芯片设计商博通合作开发先进的人工智能处理器，此举将有助于 TikTok 的所有者在中美关系紧张之际确保充足的高端芯片供应。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 03:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinas-bytedance-working-with-broadcom-develop-advanced-ai-chip-sources-say-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统在中国威胁分裂主义后表示独裁是“邪恶的”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/autocracy-is-evil-taiwan-president-says-after-china-threatens-death-separatism-2024-06-24/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周一在中国威胁要对“顽固”台独分裂分子判处死刑后表示，民主不是犯罪，独裁才是真正的“罪恶”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 02:44:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/autocracy-is-evil-taiwan-president-says-after-china-threatens-death-separatism-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>1-5月我国财政收入下降2.8%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-fiscal-revenue-drops-28-january-may-2024-06-24/</link><description>周一官方数据显示，由于需求疲软拖累经济复苏，2024年前5个月中国财政收入同比下降2.8%，较1-4月下降2.7%加速。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 02:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-fiscal-revenue-drops-28-january-may-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>随着谈判恢复，中国希望欧盟在 7 月 4 日之前取消电动汽车关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-wants-eu-scrap-ev-tariffs-evs-by-july-4-chinese-state-media-reports-2024-06-24/</link><description>据中国官方媒体《环球时报》报道，在双方同意举行新的贸易谈判后，北京希望欧盟在 7 月 4 日之前取消对中国电动汽车的初步关税。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 02:16:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-wants-eu-scrap-ev-tariffs-evs-by-july-4-chinese-state-media-reports-2024-06-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>